# .aiignore — CleanSlate AI ignore file
#
# List patterns (one per line) for files and folders that CleanSlate AI
# should NEVER touch. Supports glob-style wildcards.
#
# Examples:
#   *.key         → ignore all private key files
#   Confidential  → ignore a folder named "Confidential"
#   taxes_*       → ignore files starting with "taxes_"

# Sensitive file types (recommended defaults)
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.env
*.secret

# System / IDE folders
.vscode
.idea
node_modules
